nn an Schnitzler, [17. 1. 1908]</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01644">Schnitzler an Ehrenstein, 19. 12. 1906</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01757">Schnitzler an Ehrenstein, 24. 1. 1908</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
